    frameBorder: "0",
    allow: "accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture",
    allowFullScreen: true
  }), mdx("p", null, "This video encompasses almost everything I\u2019ve learned in the past couple of years. I will be writing much more about it. Meanwhile, here are a couple of external links about the basic subjects:"), mdx("p", null, mdx("a", {
