  }, "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=keW5xpdoL7g")), mdx("p", null, "I hear beauty, and tremendous tension. Something has to happen here, and soon \u2014 it feels like a pencil balancing on its point, ", mdx("a", {
    parentName: "p",
    "href": "http://nre509.wikidot.com/ball-well-diagrams-feedback-and-equilibria"
