  }, "gorgeous song"), " with Ravi Shankar\u2019s two daughters, Norah Jones and Anoushka Shankar. It\u2019s not drone music, but it\u2019s a beautiful blend of East and West, and I feel the purity of the notes down to my bones. This is untempered music."), mdx("p", null, "At this point I must pause again to acknowledge my enormous debt to W.A. Mathieu. I had been studying just intonation for several months when my friend Kay Ashley, a fine singer, guitarist and student of ", mdx("a", {
